{"lemma":"غَسَلاتِ","slug":"غَسَلاتِ","root":"غ.س.ل","root_slug":"غ-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31845","n31855","n31856","n31857"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of غَسَلَ (ḡasala): an instance of washing, a wash"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from the verb غَسَلَ (ḡasala)"},"ipa":["/ɣas.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31845","headword_ar":"غَسَلَهُ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolN","text_ar":"غَسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusolN","text_ar":"غُسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst, (S, Msb,) or a subst. (Mgh, K, TA) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAigotisaAlu","text_ar":"الاِغْتِسَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) or, as some say. the latter is the inf. n. and the former is the subst., (MF, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He washed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"with water ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmaA='i","text_ar":"بِالمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (MA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolu Al$~Yo'i","text_ar":"غَسْلُ الشّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the removing of dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like thereof, from the thing, by making water to run over it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala Aljiloda kul~ahu","text_ar":"غَسَلَ الجِلْدَ كُلَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He washed the skin, all of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almay~ita","text_ar":"المَيِّتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dead"},{"kind":"text","text":"body]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gs~l","text_ar":"غسّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has the like, but an intensive, meaning. (Msb.) See also 10. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@gosiloniY bimaA='i Alv~aloji waAlbaradi","text_ar":"وَا@غْسِلْنِى بِمَا=ءِ الثَّلْجِ وَالبَرَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And wash Thou me with the water of snow and of hail"},{"kind":"text","text":"], in a trad. relating to [forms of] prayer, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and cleanse Thou me from sins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala A@ll~`hu Hawobataka","text_ar":"غَسَلَ ا@للّٰهُ حَوْبَتَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God cleanse thee from thy sin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA gasaluwA ruw^uwsahumo mino","text_ar":"مَا غَسَلُوا رُوُوسَهُمْ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomi Aljamali","text_ar":"يَوْمِ الجَمَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They did not wash their heads"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., as one does in cleansing himself from impurity,] means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA faraguwA","text_ar":"مَا فَرَغُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA taxal~aSuwA","text_ar":"مَا تَخَلَّصُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., app., (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they did not become free from"},{"kind":"text","text":"the consequences of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Day of the Camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the famous engagement between the forces of 'Alee and those of Áïsheh)]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And one says of a horse,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusila","text_ar":"غُسِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sweated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became suffused with sweat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Sh, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aigotasala","text_ar":"اِغْتَسَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See an ex. of the former in a verse cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Edw","text_ar":"عدو"},{"kind":"text","text":", conj. 3.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala AlmaroA^apa","text_ar":"غَسَلَ المَرْاَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He compressed the woman"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAmaEahaA","text_ar":"جَامَعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (Az, Mgh, O, TA;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasalahaA","text_ar":"عَسَلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Az, Mgh, TA;) much or little; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gas~alahaA","text_ar":"غَسَّلَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Mgh, O, TA:) or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did so much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) It is said in a trad., (Mgh, O, TA,) respecting [preparation for the prayers of] Friday, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano gasala waA@gotasala","text_ar":"مَنْ غَسَلَ وَا@غْتَسَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as some relate it, or, as others relate it,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAgtsl","text_ar":"واغتسل"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn gas~ala","text_ar":"من غَسَّلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the latter of which is said to mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whose compresses"},{"kind":"text","text":"his wife [before his going to the mosque]; (Mgh, O;) and El-Kutabee says that most hold this to be the meaning; i. e., lest he should see in his way anything that might divert his heart [from devotion]; (Mgh;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"washes himself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and Az held"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala","text_ar":"غَسَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", without teshdeed to be correct (Mgh, O) in this sense: (Mgh:) or the meaning accord. to the reading of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gs~l","text_ar":"غسّل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose performs the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ablution termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuDuw'o","text_ar":"وُضُوءْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fully, washing every member"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those that are to be washed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three times,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"washes himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the [prayers of] Friday; (Mgh;) and accord. to IAmb, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose washes himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"after"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljimaAE","text_ar":"الجِمَاع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"washes himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the [prayers of] Friday; (O:) accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~agosiyla","text_ar":"التَّغْسِيلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the exceeding the ordinary bounds in washing the members:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) he who explains as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the causing"},{"kind":"text","text":"a woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to become under the obligation of performing a total ablution,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^ano","text_ar":"بِاَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waTiy^ahaA","text_ar":"وَطِيَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", says what is improbable, and departs from the authorities respecting it. (Mgh.) ―         -b6-  One say, also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala AlfaHolu Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"غَسَلَ الفَحْلُ النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stallion covered the she-camel much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [See also 4.] ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasala","text_ar":"غَسَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasolN","text_ar":"غَسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat, and caused to suffer pain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~awoTi","text_ar":"بِالسَّوْطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the whip"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","MA","O","Msb","K","Mgh","TA","MF"]},{"entry_id":"n31855","headword_ar":"غَسْلَةٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of washing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasalaAtN","text_ar":"غَسَلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banawoA h`*ihi Almadiynapa bigasalaAti","text_ar":"بَنَوْا هٰذِهِ المَدِينَةَ بِغَسَلَاتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayodiyhimo","text_ar":"اَيْدِيهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They built this city"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of their earnings."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31856","headword_ar":"غِسْلَةٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasuwlN","text_ar":"غَسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gisolN","text_ar":"غِسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY wajohihi gisolapN","text_ar":"عَلَى وَجْهِهِ غِسْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His face is beautiful, with no fat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatness, upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw","text_ar":"اَبُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gisolapa","text_ar":"غِسْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wolf:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abw Eisolapa","text_ar":"ابو عِسْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n31857","headword_ar":"غُسَلَةٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalN","text_ar":"غُسَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylN","text_ar":"غَسِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gis~iylN","text_ar":"غِسِّيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migosalN","text_ar":"مِغْسَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gisolN","text_ar":"غِسْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) all, except the last, mentioned by Fr, (O, TA,) applied to a stallion [camel], (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That covers much:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Mgh, * O, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that does so much without impregnating:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, S, K, TA:) and in like manner applied to a man. (K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasilN","text_ar":"غَسِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","K","TA","Ks"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}